## **9. IDS/IPS (Intrusion Detection and Prevention Systems) oâ€˜rnatish**  
Hujumni oldini olish uchun **IDS yoki IPS tizimi oâ€˜rnatish lozim**.  

### **Snort IDS orqali tarmoq monitoring qilish:**
```bash
